<p class="siDoi"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pcbi.1008837.s003">https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pcbi.1008837.s003</a></p><a id="article1.body1.sec4.supplementary-material3.caption1.p2" name="article1.body1.sec4.supplementary-material3.caption1.p2" class="link-target"></a><p class="postSiDOI">(PDF)</p>
